SIMPLE: shapeless
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Shapeless
<hw>Shape"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Destitute of shape or regular
form; wanting symmetry of dimensions; misshapen; -- opposed to
<ant>shapely</ant>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Shape"less*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>shapeless</qex> rock, or hanging precipice.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shapeliness</ent>⟦br⟧
